Class MakeSummaryTable

java.lang.Object
  MakeSummaryTable

public class MakeSummaryTable
extends java.lang.Object

This class reads the table created after reading the input file, and constructs a new table that contains the aggregate values of various attributes grouped by states and political parties. Control enters this class from the 'make' method.
